Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸被奪走的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓…子…
